OL,3,CPlans for St Helier park-and-ride to
OL,4,Cease town parking problem
OL,6,FDrivers and businesses are calling for
OL,7,Fmore to be done about parking in.
OL,9,FIt comes as figures reveal nearly a
OL,10,Fquarter of St Helier residents still
OL,11,Fdrive to work in town, despite living
OL,12,Fnearby.
OL,14,FTo tackle the problem, Infrastructure
OL,15,FMinister Andy Jehan is working on
OL,16,Fsetting up a park-and-ride scheme.
OL,18,FDrivers say they are trying to find
OL,19,Fparking spaces in St Helier an hour
OL,20,Fbefore they start their working day.
