OL,3,CPlans for St Helier park-and-ride to
OL,4,Cease town parking problem
OL,6,FOne says: "You used to be able to park
OL,7,Fin Green Street up until about nine in
OL,8,Fthe morning but now you'll be lucky if
OL,9,Fyou get a space by 8:45am and all the
OL,10,Fother long-stay car parks are usually
OL,11,Ffull now, apart from Pier Road."
OL,13,FAnother adds that public transport is
OL,14,Fnot an option for them: "I live in
OL,15,FGorey, I could get a bus but it takes
OL,16,Fa longer time and it's less convenient
OL,17,Fif I have to pop out."
OL,19,FNeila Frango, a flower shop manager,
OL,20,Fsays the problem is having a knock-on
OL,21,Feffect on her business.
