OL,3,CPlans for St Helier park-and-ride to
OL,4,Cease town parking problem
OL,6,FShe explains: "We have a driver who
OL,7,Fcomes around to park, he can't find
OL,8,Fparking, then he has to go all the way
OL,9,Faround town which takes him forever to
OL,10,Fcome back because of all the road
OL,11,Fclosures as well. It is just to load
OL,12,Fup and it's just a nightmare."
OL,14,FHowever, climate campaigner Nigel
OL,15,FJones says people should stop relying
OL,16,Fon driving.
