OL,3,CPlans for St Helier park-and-ride to
OL,4,Cease town parking problem
OL,6,FHe says: "People just assume that they
OL,7,Fhave to get in a car and drive. People
OL,8,Fwill have to learn that we're not made
OL,9,Fof candy sticks, we won't melt if you
OL,10,Fgo out in the rain and it's not really
OL,11,Fthat cold if you put your big coat on
OL,12,Fand get walking."
OL,14,FConstable Jehan says it is important
OL,15,Fnot to restrict islanders: "It's
OL,16,Faround convenience, it's about giving
OL,17,Fpeople choices and options. I don't
OL,18,Fthink you can take away ownership of
OL,19,Fcars from people.
