OL,3,CPlans for St Helier park-and-ride to
OL,4,Cease town parking problem
OL,6,F"We need to make it easier for people
OL,7,Fto use the hopper bus and there is
OL,8,Fgoing to be some exciting news on that
OL,9,Fin a couple of weeks.
OL,11,F"I'm working with the Constable of St
OL,12,FHelier. We're looking to identify
OL,13,Fsites on the outskirts of St Helier to
OL,14,Fprovide additional parking.
OL,16,F"Whilst we want to encourage people to
OL,17,Fuse bikes and buses, it's also
OL,18,Fimportant that we provide sufficient
OL,19,Fparking."
